WEB SERVERS
===============================================================================================================================

-> Python2
$ python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8080

-> Python3
$ python3 -m http.server 8080

-> Ruby
$ ruby -run -ehttpd . -p8080

-> PHP
$ php -S 0.0.0.0:8080

-> SOCAT
$ socat TCP-LISTEN:8080,reuseaddr,fork

-> IIS (Windows, Administrative access)
PS C:\directory> Add-WindowsFeature Web-Server, Web-Mgmt-Tools
